# Normalize line endings to LF for all text files, regardless of OS.
# This repo is developed on Windows (D: drive) — without this, editors/tools
# that write CRLF cause every line of a touched file to show as changed in
# git diffs, even when content is identical. See docs/adr/ for context if a
# future stage needs an exception for a specific file type.
* text=auto eol=lf
